    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctę et individuę Trinitatis. <persName key="#Princeps"
                            ref="#people/339">Guaimarius</persName> divina fabente clementia <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> Salerni et Capuę et <rs
                            key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> Amalfitanorum. Quoniam oportet nos
                        sanctorum locorum curam gerere et eisdem venerabilibus locis iuste petita
                        tribuere, <rs key="#Intercessory">per interventu</rs> domni <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2449" key="#Intercessory #Abbots">Richerii</persName>
                        et sanctorum fratrum devotissime Deo <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/84"
                            key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Property_of_persons_without_heirs #Monasteries"
                            >in sancto Casinati</orgName> servientium <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>, concedo eidem monasterio, pro amore Dei omnipotentis
                        et sancti Benedicti eximii abbatis, omnes <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terras</rs> et <rs key="#Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >hereditates</rs> et <rs key="#Fundi">predia</rs> que id ipsum
                        monasterium et eidem monasterio subiectę ecclesię possident <placeName
                            ref="#places/4516"
                            key="#Fundi #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Function #Redistributive #Inflow #Inheritance #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >in valle Cumini</placeName>, et quę deinceps habitatores eiusdem vallis
                        de suis rebus oblaturi sunt suprascripto monasterio et ęcclesiis ei
                        subiectis, quatenus liceat rectores suprascripti monasterii iam dictas res
                        securiter habere et de eis quę iuste voluerint agere sine omni cuiuslibet
                        contrarietate personę. Siquis autem huius nostrę concessionis temerarius
                        violator extiterit, noverit se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">.X(m). libras
                            auri</rs>, dimidium nostrę camere et dimidium rectoribus prenominati
                        monasterii. Quod ut verius credatur atque confirmetur, anuli nostri
                        impressione id preceptum iussimus insigniri.</ab>
                </div>
